                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">through an interpreter</hi>). I am a seaman, lodging in Well-close-square, in the same house with the prisoner; we both slept in one room—when I went to bed I laid my jacket and waistcoat on the bed, and when I awoke they were gone, and the prisoner was gone also—I have never seen them since—there were no other persons in the room.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18541218-name-172" type="witnessName">
